deployAssetPool((address,uint8,bytes4[]).details: Transfers ownership to the controller and initializes access control.

params._facets: Asset Pool facets for the factory diamond to deploy.
params._registry: Registry address to point the pool to.

params._pool: Address of pool that should be registered.

deployAssetPool((address,uint8,bytes4[]).notice: Deploys and stores the reference to an asset pool based on the current defaultCut.

registerAssetPool(address).notice: Registers a pool address in the internal register. Only accessible for diamond owner.

setDefaultController(address).notice: Sets the controller for the factory diamond.
